README amass-bin

CONFIGURATION

	See /etc/amass/config.ini for configuration details.

	The location of the configuration file can be specified using the
	-config flag or the AMASS_CONFIG environment variable.

	Amass automatically tries to discover the configuration file (named
	config.ini) in the following locations:

		* $XDG_CONFIG_HOME/amass/config.ini
		* $HOME/.config/amass/config.ini
		* /etc/amass/config.ini

End of file.
